@baseUrl = http://127.0.0.1:8080
@adminUsername = admin
@ownerUsername = wang_jie
@employeeUsername = chen_xu
@password = 123456
@targetProjectId = 2
@targetNodeId = 2
@completedProjectId = 1
@completedNodeId = 1
@missingProjectId = 999999
@missingNodeId = 999999
@invalidProjectId = 0
@invalidNodeId = 0

### 提示：正常路径会写入数据库；当前使用固定节点反复写入相同值，便于重复回放。
### 提示：project 2（移动端打卡）下的 node 2（原型设计）为未完成节点；project 1 下的 node 1（需求分析）为已完成节点。
### 当前为 12.4 修改阶段节点基础信息 的先行失败用例；接口未实现前，相关请求会先失败，后续据此补实现。

### 正常路径：管理员登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：管理员修改阶段节点基础信息
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "原型设计阶段",
  "description": "用于验证阶段节点基础信息修改接口。",
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-10",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-18"
}

### 正常路径：管理员登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：未登录修改阶段节点基础信息，预期 401
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "未登录修改阶段节点。"
}

### 正常路径：负责人登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{ownerUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 正常路径：负责人修改自己项目下的阶段节点基础信息
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "用于验证负责人修改阶段节点基础信息。"
}

### 正常路径：负责人登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 正常路径：普通员工登录
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{employeeUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：普通员工修改非本人负责项目下的阶段节点，预期 403
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "普通员工尝试修改非本人负责项目下的阶段节点。"
}

### 正常路径：普通员工登出
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/logout
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：重新登录管理员
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "{{adminUsername}}",
  "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 异常路径：project_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{invalidProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "非法项目ID"
}

### 异常路径：node_id 小于等于 0，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{invalidNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "非法节点ID"
}

### 异常路径：请求体不是 JSON 对象，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

[
  {
    "name": "invalid_body_case"
  }
]

### 异常路径：请求体没有可修改字段，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{}

### 异常路径：name 不是字符串，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": 123
}

### 异常路径：name 为空字符串，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": ""
}

### 异常路径：planned_start_date 格式错误，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planned_start_date": "2026/04/10"
}

### 异常路径：planned_end_date 格式错误，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planned_end_date": "2026/04/18"
}

### 异常路径：同时修改开始和结束日期且区间非法，预期 409
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "planned_start_date": "2026-04-19",
  "planned_end_date": "2026-04-18"
}

### 异常路径：只传 status 和 completed_at，因没有可修改字段，预期 400
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 2,
  "completed_at": "2026-04-18T10:00:00+08:00"
}

### 异常路径：已完成阶段节点修改基础信息，预期 409
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{completedProjectId}}/nodes/{{completedNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "尝试修改已完成阶段节点。"
}

### 异常路径：项目不存在，预期 404
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{missingProjectId}}/nodes/{{targetNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "不存在项目。"
}

### 异常路径：阶段节点不存在，预期 404
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/projects/{{targetProjectId}}/nodes/{{missingNodeId}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "不存在阶段节点。"
}
